{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "第六回　锋镝情潮：本章围绕主要人物的遭遇、江湖见闻与冲突推进展开。第六回锋镝情潮马一进当涂，就走得慢了，熊倜只见家家户户，都贴着大红春联，店铺虽都关起了门不做生意，但门口都站着大人小孩，放鞭炮，吃春饼，穿的是新做的衣裳。熊倜和夏芸骑在马上，夏芸指东指西，叽叽咕咕讲个不停，又说又笑，引得路上的人都驻足而望，奇怪这美貌的少女怎会和这像叫化子似的人同乘一骑，而又那么亲热。夏芸娇嗔道：\"这些人坏死了，死盯着我章节中人物往来、言语试探和武林局势互相交织，为后续恩怨、师承与行动埋下线索。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，我说你换件衣服好不好，不要老是这样嘛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人家上了门，我们不会去敲他他们的门吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们想买几件衣服，要特别好的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不卖也得卖，我出双倍的价钱，还不行吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这胖子莫非是长江渡头那两个诡异客商的兄弟……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位掌柜的，可是姓叶？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么会认识这样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事呀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样也好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ubldp_ubrgr_chang",
      "speaker_name": "我爹常",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她说着眼圈都红了，又说：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不知道为什么，把什么话都告诉你了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我爹爹说当年他也是保镖的呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看看有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么东西都可以看，就是这镖旗，却随便看不得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我偏看不可！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不要拉我，我一定要教训教训那家伙。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "算了，算了，我们又何必跟那种人一般见识。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有什么，只是一点小事罢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些都是些什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些人都是近年来在武林中赫赫一时的人物，'一异'就是天阴教主焦异行夫妇，'双绝'是峨嵋的孤峰一剑边浩和江苏虎丘的出尘剑客，飞灵堡主东方灵……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道这位便是雪地飘风吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小弟还有些事情，少陪了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你别骗我，下次我再也不受你的骗了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然啦。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不怪我啦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "熊兄别开玩笑了，熊兄若不知道，还有谁人知道？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "史兄这话却怎的讲法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这可真吓死我了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那真太好了，我先谢谢姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人家既然已经来赔话了，你就还给人家吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 437,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你别拦着我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也是的，人家……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 453,
      "line_end": 453
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你走，你走，我永远不要听你说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个只有到时候再说了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "便是这家了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还敲什么门，大家一起越墙而入好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这熊倜果然厉害，竟已知道了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 581,
      "line_end": 581
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夏姑娘真是快人快语，那么就请姑娘跟着我来吧。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 597,
      "line_end": 597
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "收拾你这种黄毛丫头，还用得着别人费事？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 629,
      "line_end": 629
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "东方灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王兄且慢动手，我还有几句问她。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 633,
      "line_end": 633
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 639,
      "line_end": 639
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁要你让，你若不动手，我也不动手。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 681,
      "line_end": 681
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么小心了。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 683,
      "line_end": 683
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是宝马神鞭萨天骥的什么人？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 687,
      "line_end": 687
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁认识萨天骥！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 689,
      "line_end": 689
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是教训教训你，让你知道人外有人，不要卖狂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 721,
      "line_end": 721
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你少哕嗦。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 723,
      "line_end": 723
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像你这样的脾气，早晚要吃大亏……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 743,
      "line_end": 743
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位姑娘应该怎么发落？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 755,
      "line_end": 755
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是死了，也不跟你们一起去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 781,
      "line_end": 781
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位就饶了她吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 783,
      "line_end": 783
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看他的身法影子，我想一定是熊倜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 797,
      "line_end": 797
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "熊倜，熊倜……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 799,
      "line_end": 799
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要紧的，等一会就好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 813,
      "line_end": 813
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不是曾经给你一枚古钱为记吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 881,
      "line_end": 881
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 883,
      "line_end": 883
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好朋友居然不买账。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 937,
      "line_end": 937
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "深夜打扰，实非得已，皆因敝友在无意中得罪了武当四子，受了重伤，小弟又因故不能和武当四子照面，是以必须寻一妥当之处，为敝友疗伤，小弟在此人地生疏，突然想起贵兄弟义薄云天，故此不嫌冒昧就闯来了",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 967,
      "line_end": 967
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "叶老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我自顾高兴，竟忘了替你们引见了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 995,
      "line_end": 995
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "叶老二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你把朝南的那间书房拾收一下，夏女侠就暂时住在那里好了，书房的那间房间，就暂时委屈熊兄一下，正好照应夏女侠，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1027,
      "line_end": 1027
    }
  ],
